from browser import document, window
from heavy_stack_brython.scrolling import scroll_to_element

kwargs = {'delay': 0, 'js_id': 'time-at-top'}

data_storage = document.getElementById("12d5f928b2454dc99c278be2e07fff3b")

def signal_complete(result = ""):
    data_storage.value = result
    event = window.Event.new("input")
    data_storage.dispatchEvent(event)

result = scroll_to_element(signal_complete, **kwargs)
